OL,3,CFormer mineworkers receive pension
OL,4,Cboost
OL,6,FFormer mineworkers are receiving on
OL,7,Faverage an extra #100 to their weekly
OL,8,Fpension payment from today.
OL,10,FThe move follows the Chancellor's
OL,11,Fannouncement at the Budget that the
OL,12,F#2.3 billion reserve, previously held
OL,13,Fby Government since 1994, is being
OL,14,Ftransferred to members of the British
OL,15,FCoal Staff Superannuation Scheme
OL,16,F(BCSSS).
