OL,3,CFormer mineworkers receive pension
OL,4,Cboost
OL,6,FMinisters said that with payments
OL,7,Fbackdated to November 2024 when the
OL,8,Fincrease to the Mineworkers' Pension
OL,9,FScheme was implemented, members should
OL,10,Ftoday receive a #5,500 lump sum on
OL,11,Faverage.
OL,13,FThe BCSSS scheme represents former
OL,14,Fcoal miners as well as those who
OL,15,Fworked in non-mining roles at
OL,16,Fcollieries across the UK ` including
OL,17,Fengineers, managers, canteen workers
OL,18,Fand administrators.
OL,20,FMore than 4,000 of those to receive
OL,21,Fthe boost are in the North East.
