OL,3,CFormer mineworkers receive pension
OL,4,Cboost
OL,6,FFormer miner Stuart Porthouse, from
OL,7,FCounty Durham, told ITV News: "We've
OL,8,Fbeen fighting to try and get
OL,9,Frecognised.
OL,11,F"And it's a relief at last, because
OL,12,Fover the last year we've lost a lot of
OL,13,Four members. They have gone, but
OL,14,Ffortunately the government have agreed
OL,15,Fthat they'll be backpaid into their
OL,16,Festate, which is a good thing."
