OL,3,CFormer mineworkers receive pension
OL,4,Cboost
OL,6,FSecretary of State for Energy and Net
OL,7,FZero Ed Miliband said: "I want to pay
OL,8,Ftribute to all the mineworkers and all
OL,9,Fthe campaigners involved in ending
OL,10,Fthis decades-long injustice.
OL,12,F"Today, thousands will rightly see a
OL,13,F41% uplift in their pension payment
OL,14,Fjust before Christmas ` providing them
OL,15,Fwith the retirement they deserve."
