OL,3,CFormer mineworkers receive pension
OL,4,Cboost
OL,6,FCheryl Agius, chair of trustees of the
OL,7,FBritish Coal Staff Superannuation
OL,8,FScheme, said: "This is a historic
OL,9,Fmoment ` the result of a year of
OL,10,Fdetermination, advocacy and
OL,11,Fcollaboration ` and it marks a turning
OL,12,Fpoint for the scheme.
OL,14,F"The Government has listened to the
OL,15,Ftrustees, scheme members, and
OL,16,Fcoalfield MPs that have supported this
OL,17,Fissue, and agreed to transfer the
OL,18,Fscheme's investment reserve to members.
