OL,6,F"Being able to make the first bonus
OL,7,Fpension increase today brings BCSSS
OL,8,Fmembers into line with their former
OL,9,Fcolleagues in the Mineworkers' Pension
OL,10,FScheme (MPS), who received their
OL,11,Finvestment reserve in November last
OL,12,Fyear."
